quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  17,50,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ di òkúta tàbí irin.",""
  17,51,"Tàbí (kí ẹ di) ẹ̀dá kan nínú ohun tí ó tóbi nínú ọkàn yín.” Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ wọn yóò wí pé: “Ta ni Ó máa dá wa padà (fún àjíǹde)?” Sọ pé: “Ẹni tí Ó pilẹ̀ ìṣẹ̀dá yín ní ìgbà àkọ́kọ́ ni.” Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ wọn yóò mi orí wọn sí ọ (ní ti àbùkù). Nígbà náà, wọn yóò wí pé: “Ìgbà wo ni?” Sọ pé: “Ó lè jẹ́ pé ó ti súnmọ́.”",""
  17,52,"Ọjọ́ tí Allāhu yóò pè yín. Ẹ sì máa jẹ́pè pẹ̀lú ẹyìn Rẹ̀. Ẹ sì máa lérò pé ẹ kò gbé ilé ayé bí kò ṣe fún ìgbà díẹ̀.",""
  17,53,"Sọ fún àwọn ẹrúsìn Mi pé kí wọ́n máa sọ èyí tó dára jùlọ (nínú ọ̀rọ̀). Dájúdájú aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n yóò máa dá yánpọn-yánrin sílẹ̀ láààrin wọn. Dájúdájú aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n jẹ́ ọ̀tá pọ́nńbélé fún ènìyàn.",""
  17,54,"Olúwa yín nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa yín. Tí Ó bá fẹ́, Ó máa kẹ yín. Tàbí tí Ó bá sì fẹ́, Ó máa jẹ yín níyà. A kò rán ọ pé kí o jẹ́ olùṣọ́ lórí wọn.",""
  17,55,"Olúwa rẹ nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa àwọn tó ń bẹ nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀. Dájúdájú A ti ṣe oore àjùlọ fún apá kan àwọn Ànábì lórí apá kan. A sì fún (Ànábì) Dāwūd ní Zabūr.",""
  17,56,"Sọ pé: “Ẹ pe àwọn tí ẹ sọ nípa wọn - láì ní ẹ̀rí lọ́wọ́ - pé wọ́n jẹ́ ọlọ́hun lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀, (ẹ máa rí i pé) wọn kò ní ìkápá láti gbé ìnira kúrò tàbí láti ṣe ìyípadà kan fún yín.”",""
  17,57,"Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn tí wọ́n ń pè (lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀) ń wá àtẹ̀gùn sọ́dọ̀ Olúwa wọn ni! - Èwo nínú wọn ló súnmọ́ (Allāhu) jùlọ (báyìí)? - Àwọn náà ń retí ìkẹ́ Allāhu, wọ́n sì ń páyà ìyà Rẹ̀. Dájúdájú ìyà Olúwa rẹ jẹ́ ohun tí wọ́n gbọ́dọ̀ ṣọ́ra fún.",""
  17,58,"Kò sí ìlú kan (tó ṣàbòsí) àfi kí Àwa pa á rẹ́ ṣíwájú Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde tàbí kí Á jẹ ẹ́ níyà líle. Ìyẹn ti wà ní kíkọ sílẹ̀ nínú Tírà (Laohul-Mahfūṭḥ).",""
